<article id="article" class="article "><header><h1 class="title" itemprop="headline">The City of Music</h1>

					<p class="dek">Bill Whitaker travels to Cremona, the medieval Italian city that gave the world the famed Stradivarius violin</p>
		
    </header><div class="social sharebar_expanded inline-sharebar theme-light  location-top" data-component="sharebar">

